(4, 'India lost its Top ODI Rank', 'india-lost-its-top-odi-rank', 'India vs New Zealand Live Cricket Update - India tour of New Zealand 2014', 'India vs New Zealand, Live Cricket news, India tour of New Zealand 2014, India losing top ODI rank, india, New Zealand', 'India vs New Zealand Live Cricket Update - India tour of New Zealand 2014. India losing top ODI rank with 0-2 against New Zealand', '11823064471688193149.jpg', '<p>\r\n	India slipped its ODI rank battling against New Zealand in 2nd ODI which was played on 22nd January, 2014. <strong>India tour of New Zealand 2014</strong> begun from 19<sup>th</sup> January 2014 as per the cricket schedule announced by the Indian Cricket Broad. The series of India and New Zealand will be called as International Bilateral Series, India tour of New Zealand 2014 series is a part of FTP (Future Cricket Tour programs) prepared by ICC (International Cricket Council). India tour of New Zealand 2014 series will play in New Zealand in which 5 ODI and 2 test matches will be played between India and New Zealand from 19<sup>th</sup> January 2014 to 18<sup>th</sup> February 2014.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>India vs New Zealand</strong> 1<sup>st</sup> ODI will be played on Sunday 19<sup>th</sup> January 2014 at Mclean Park in Napier. All the 5 ODI of India vs. New Zealand will be played day/night starting at Local GMT 01:00 hrs. Local New Zealand time 14:00 hrs. and Indian time 06:30. The 2<sup>nd</sup> and the 4<sup>th</sup> ODI matches of <strong>New Zealand vs. India 2014 series</strong> will be played in Hamilton on 22<sup>nd</sup> January and 28<sup>th</sup> January 2014, whereas the 3<sup>rd</sup> one day International cricket match between <strong>India vs. New Zealand</strong> will be played on 25<sup>th</sup> January 2014 in Auckland followed by the 5<sup>th</sup> and last ODI of India vs. New Zealand series will be played on 31<sup>st</sup> January 2014 in Wellington. India vs. New Zealand 2014 test series wi