(9, 'beIN Sports', 'bein-sports-live-streaming-watch-live-sports-on-bein-live-channels', 'beIN Sports Live Streaming Watch Live Sports on beIN Live Channels', 'BEIN Sports Live Streaming, BEIN Sports, Al Jazeera channel, Watch soccer, nba, nfl, nhl, football, tennis, cricket channels, beIN Sports 1, beIN Sports 2, beIN Sports MAX, bein HD', 'beIN Sports Live Streaming. Watch BEIN Sports Live Al Jazeera Media. Watch soccer, nba, nfl, nhl, football, tennis, cricket channels on beIN Sports 1, beIN Sports 2 and beIN Sports MAX in HD', '1519678900541453129.jpg', '<p>\r\n	<strong>beIN Sports Live Streaming</strong>: <b>BEIN Sports</b> is jointly operated by <strong>Qatari Sports Investments</strong> affiliated to Al Jazeera Media Networks. beIN Sports is a international network of sports channels all around the world. It has three channels in France called <strong>beIN Sports 1, beIN Sports 2</strong> and <strong>beIN Sports MAX</strong>. In the year 2012 <strong>Al Jazeera Media Network</strong> beIN Sports has launched two more channels of sports in United States in English and Spanish. beIN Sports Network also has the broadcast rights to telecast sports in Canada, beside that they already started the online <strong>live streaming</strong> <strong>football</strong> and other sports in Canada from October 2013. <strong>Watch beIN Sports channel</strong> is known for broadcasting Association Football Tournament in France, the list of major tournaments that broadcast by beIN Sports are <strong>Bundesliga</strong>, European Football Championships, Ligue 1 and <strong>UEFA Champions League</strong>. <b>Live Soccer</b> telecasted all games in HD of all leagues and international soccer tournaments.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	beIN Sports live streaming is available to residents of Canada and United States for all the major league sports. beIN Sports also has broadcast rights to telecast sports in Canada and United States for the following tournaments; <strong>Ligue 1, South America World Cup Qualifier, Serie A</strong>, <strong>La Liga, Copa del Rey</strong>, and <strong>English Championship matches</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	beIN Sports has official broadcasting right in Indonesia also to broadcast the major tournament such as Ligue 1 of France, Italian Serie A, <strong>Major League Soccer</strong> (MLS) along with three season <strong>English Premier League</strong> matches from 2013-14 to 2015-16. And same in Hong Kong as well beIN Sports hold the right of broadcast the Football tournaments along with Milan TV, Liverpool TV and Spurs TV.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Al Jazeera Network channel beIN Sports not only broadcast football but also other International sports such as Superbike World Championship, Team Handball and <strong>live Rugby</strong> matches. beIN Sports will broadcast all the French Rugby team home matches along with Super League and other competitions. beIN Sports also broadcast <strong>live Rugby</strong> matches such as <strong>National Rugby League</strong> and <strong>State of Origin series</strong> of Australia along with other International Rugby competitions. beIN Sports also host <strong>live streaming rugby</strong> and football matches on their official website.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	BEIN Sports is dominated by the <a href=\\"http://football.watchcriclive.com\\" title=\\"live football\\"><strong>live football</strong></a> coverage on their sports channels. To cover all the Premier League and Major Tournament of Football beIN Sports has dedicate channels like <strong>beIN Sports 1 HD</strong> which will focus on live football match with <strong>Barclay&rsquo;s Premier League</strong> as they main tournament and other live football of Italy and French. beIN Sports 2 HD will also cover the live football match along with live Rugby. In Indonesia <strong>Al Jazeera Sports Network</strong> has a dedicated <strong>beIN Sports Premier League HD</strong> channel which will telecast <strong>Live English Premier League</strong> matches 24-hours.</p>\r\n', '0.64', '2014-02-14 10:38:27', 'Active'),
