Live</a> on 2nd March, 2014 at 08:00 GMT.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<strong>T20 World Cup</strong>: 13th T20 - <a href=\\"http://cricket.watchcriclive.com/13th-t20-india-vs-pakistan-live-streaming/208\\" title=\\"india vs pakistan live\\">India vs Pakistan Live</a> on 21st March, 2014 at 13:30 GMT.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div id=\\"stcpDiv\\" style=\\"position: absolute; top: -1999px; left: -1988px;\\">\r\n	6th ODI - India vs Pakistan</div>\r\n<div id=\\"stcpDiv\\" style=\\"position: absolute; top: -1999px; left: -1988px;\\">\r\n	6th ODI - India vs Pakistan</div>\r\n<div id=\\"stcpDiv\\" style=\\"position: absolute; top: -1999px; left: -1988px;\\">\r\n	6th ODI - India vs Pakistan</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Indian Squad</strong>: Vijay Zol, Ankush Bains, Avesh Khan, Ricky Bhui, Aamir Gani, Akhil Herwadkar, Deepak Hooda, Shreyas Iyer, Karan Kaila, Sarfaraz Khan, Kuldeep Yadav, Chama Milind, Monu Kumar, Sanju Samson and Atit Sheth</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Pakistan Squad</strong>: Sami Aslam, Amad Butt, Ameer Hamza, Hasan Raza, Hussain Talat, Imam-ul-Haq, Imran Rafiq, Kamran Ghulam, Irfanullah Shah, Karamat Ali, Zafar Gohar, Mohammad Aftab, Saifullah Khan, Saud Shakeel and Zia-ul-Haq</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><font face=\\"arial\\" size=\\"5\\" variant=\\"small-caps\\"><a href=\\"http://www.watchlivestreaming.net\\" onclick=\\"window.open(\\''http://cricketzonem.blogspot.com\\'');\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">CLICK TO WATCH INDIA vs PAKISTAN LIVE</a></font></b></p>\r\n', '0.64', '2014-02-15 05:53:33', 'Active'),
(11, 'India vs Pakistan Live', 'india-vs-pakistan-live-streaming-watch-ind-vs-pak-live-cricket-streaming-online', 'India vs Pakistan Live Streaming Watch IND vs PAK Live Cricket Streaming Online', 'India vs Pakistan Live Streaming, Watch, IND vs PAK, Live Cricket Streaming, t20 world cup live', 'India vs Pakistan Live Streaming Watch IND vs PAK Live Cricket Streaming Online Broadcast Free on Internet Telecast by Star Sports and Willow HD T20 World Cup 2014', '315745348493180877.jpg', '<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	<b data-mce-style="line-height: 1.5em;" style="line-height: 1.5em;">India vs Pakistan Live Streaming</b>: <b>India vs Pakistan live cricket match</b> on <span data-mce-style="line-height: 1.5em;" style="line-height: 1.5em;">21 March 2014, live from Bangla National Stadium, Mirpur begins at 13:30 GMT, 19:00 IST. India will be playing against Pakistan in the 13</span><sup data-mce-style="line-height: 1.5em;" style="line-height: 1.5em;">th</sup><span data-mce-style="line-height: 1.5em;" style="line-height: 1.5em;"> T20 match of T20 World Cup 2014.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	<b>India</b> who has won their first match of the tournament against <b>Bangladesh</b> in which India won the toss and putting Bangladesh into match restricted them to a total of 279 runs and chase them down easily with a super hundred score by Indian skipper <b>Virat Kohli</b>.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	In the previous match of India lost to Sri Lanka in the 4<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;ODI match of Asia Cup. Sri Lanka won the toss and put India into bat restricted them to a score of 264 as Indian middle order failed to perform, missing their senior play including regular skipper&nbsp;<b>MS Dhoni</b>. Indian opner Shikhar Dhawan was the only batman to score runs (94 runs) on board handy supported by skipper Virat Kohli.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>Live Streaming</strong> info: <a href="http://cricket.watchcriclive.com/13th-t20-india-vs-pakistan-live-streaming/208" title="india vs pakistan live"><strong>INDIA vs PAKISTAN LIVE STREAMING</strong></a></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	In an interview after match Indian captain Virat Kohli said to the media that, the toss played a crucial role in the match, it&rsquo;s just a matter of luck. The result of the match might be different if they would have won the toss.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	<b>Pakistan</b>&nbsp;the defending champions of Asia Cup on other side are struggling holds their position in the tournament. Pakistan who lost their first match of the tournament against Sri Lanka falling short of 12 runs while chasing a target of 297 runs to win.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	Pakistan won their second match against Afghanistan with a difference of 72 runs in which Pakistan inform batsman&nbsp;<b>Umar Akmal</b>&nbsp;played a fantastic innings of 102 runs in just 89 balls to put his team in a strong position to defend.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	Pakistan skipper&nbsp;<b>Misbah-ul-Haq</b>&nbsp;is might be a bit concern about the team performance as only couple of player in the team are performing as seen in the match against Afghanistan where half of the side was down for just 117 runs.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	<b>India vs Pakistan</b>&nbsp;is a highly expected game for the both the teams and countries. India and Pakistan are having equal points on the table and will be looking forward to win&nbsp;<b>Ind vs Pak</b>&nbsp;match to secure their position in the tournament.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	<b>India vs Pakistan</b>&nbsp;match tickets are sold-out well in advance as the cricket fans of both the teams living in Bangladesh and all around the world bought the tickets well in Advance to enjoy the&nbsp;<b>live cricket</b>&nbsp;action in the ground.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	In last year Asia Cup India vs Pakistan math was played on 18<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;March 2012 in which Pakistan batting first given a target of 330 runs to India, which was easily chased down by the Indian Cricket Team. Virat Kohli was declared as Man of the Match who score fantastic innings of 183 runs in 148 balls with 22 fours and 1 six.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;">\r\n	India vs Pakistan live cricket match will be telecast on the official sports channel and media partner channel of&nbsp;<b>Asia Cup 2014</b>. Fans of both the teams are eagerly waiting for the match to be played on 6<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;March 2014.&nbsp;<b>Live cricket streaming</b>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<b>live cricket score</b>&nbsp;are available on the official website of Asia Cup.</p>\r\n', '0.64', '2014-03-02 06:35:30', 'Active');

